      "fields": [
        { "type": "note", "tone": "info", "content": "ℹ PASI (Psoriasis Area & Severity Index) is the validated severity score for psoriasis. Score each of 4 body regions: Area (0–6) × sum of Erythema + Induration + Scaling (each 0–4). Weighted total = PASI 0–72." },
